query:
INSERT INTO users (
                    uid,
                    name,
                    picture_url
                )
                VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3
                )
                ON CONFLICT (uid) DO UPDATE SET
                    name = EXCLUDED.name,
                    picture_url = EXCLUDED.picture_url
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: UserId",
                    uid,
                    name,
                    picture_url
